      <title>Elliott 提出 53 亿美元收购 Citgo 的新报价，但交易遭遇强烈反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/elliott-floats-new-5-3-billion-citgo-bid-as-deal-faces-backlash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃利奥特投资管理公司 (Elliott Investment Management) 的一家附属公司提出了收购石油炼制商 Citgo Petroleum Corp. 的替代报价，此举旨在解决对其初始报价日益增多的批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/elliott-floats-new-5-3-billion-citgo-bid-as-deal-faces-backlash</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 21:16:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普赢得驱逐计划后私人监狱股票飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/private-prison-stocks-soar-after-trump-win-on-deportation-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[私人监狱股价周三和周四飙升，因为这些公司瞄准了当选总统唐纳德·特朗普承诺实施美国历史上最大规模的移民拘留和驱逐行动所带来的潜在利润。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/private-prison-stocks-soar-after-trump-win-on-deportation-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 21:12:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔称不允许降级美联储主席和理事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/powell-demotion-of-fed-chair-governors-not-permitted-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，法律不允许解雇或降职美联储主席或其他理事。他在美联储决策机构联邦公开市场委员会一致决定将联邦基金利率下调至 4.5% 至 4.75% 区间后的新闻发布会上发表讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/powell-demotion-of-fed-chair-governors-not-permitted-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 21:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的里德预计美联储 12 月将再次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/blackrock-s-rieder-sees-fed-cutting-again-in-december-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德全球固定收益首席投资官预计美联储将在 12 月再次降息。他还谈到了特朗普政府领导下的美联储可以采取的行动。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/blackrock-s-rieder-sees-fed-cutting-again-in-december-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 20:58:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普2.0时代安全与防御</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/safety-and-defense-under-trump-2-0-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人们对当选总统唐纳德·特朗普第二任期内的科技和国防政策仍存有疑问。Anduril 创始人帕尔默·卢基与卡罗琳·海德和埃德·卢德洛一起在“彭博科技”节目上进行讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/safety-and-defense-under-trump-2-0-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 20:46:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔称即使特朗普要求他辞职他也不会辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/fed-s-powell-says-he-won-t-resign-if-trump-asks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，如果当选总统唐纳德·特朗普要求他辞职，他不会辞职。他在美联储决策机构联邦公开市场委员会一致决定将联邦基金利率下调至 4.5% 至 4.75% 区间后举行的新闻发布会上发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/fed-s-powell-says-he-won-t-resign-if-trump-asks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 20:43:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>住房贷款市场竞争加剧，澳新银行利润下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/anz-profit-drops-as-competition-bites-in-home-lending-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳新银行集团控股有限公司的利润低于预期，首席执行官 Shayne Elliott 表示抵押贷款市场的竞争仍然激烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/anz-profit-drops-as-competition-bites-in-home-lending-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 20:40:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行的罗伯茨讨论裁员、战略、美国关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/hsbc-s-roberts-says-first-round-of-job-losses-in-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰银行新成立的全球批发银行部门主管表示，该行将寻求“迅速”完成正在进行的重组，并可能在几周内宣布第一轮裁员。迈克尔·罗伯茨 (Michael Roberts) 接受彭博社 Manus Cranny 采访时谈到了该行的重组。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/hsbc-s-roberts-says-first-round-of-job-losses-in-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 19:10:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
